data.description: This modern home in The Cottages at Governor's Landing has all of the comfortable conveniences and technology you love in a newer home - in a community on the water! This five bedroom, three bathroom floor plan maximizes space with a bright and sunny formal dining room at the entry and a spacious kitchen open to the living room and eat-in kitchen area. The kitchen features a large island, walk in pantry, and granite countertops. Cozy up to the gas fireplace on chilly evenings! Main level also includes one bedroom and full bathroom. Upstairs you'll find an expansive primary suite with a well appointed ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. Additionally there are three more bedrooms, a third full bathroom, and a bonus space - perfect for a playroom, office or second living area! Modern conveniences include 'smart' light switches and endless hot water with a tankless water heater. Outside is where the fun begins! This home is on one of the biggest lots in the neighborhood at half an acre, with incredible neighborhood amenities including private boat ramp access, a clubhouse, and swimming pool. The clubhouse features a fitness center and rec space where you can get to know your neighbors and invite your friends! With an easy 13 minute drive to downtown Knoxville and the University of Tennessee's campus this home has it all!
